T02D1436:233a-1: sa ha dza sam ba ra s'a dha nam /
T02D1436:233a-3: bde mchog lhan cig skyes pa'i sgrub thabs //
T02D1436:233a-4: 'khor lo sdom pa la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D1436:233a-5: shes bya rnal 'byor cho ga gsum //
T02D1436:233a-6: byin gyis rlob dang rab tu rtog / bsam bral gzugs brnyan yongs su rdzogs //
T02D1436:233a-7: sangs rgyas kyis gsungs rnal 'byor du ;
T02D1436:233a-8: / sems can rdzus te skyes pa bzhin //
T02D1436:233a-9: gang zhig skad cig sbyor ba yis //
T02D1436:233a-10: sa bon med par rnam par bsgom //
T02D1436:233a-11: rang nyid rdo rje mkha' 'gror gyur //
T02D1436:233a-12: zla ba phyed pa spyi bor 'dzin //
T02D1436:233a-13: dpral bar thod pa'i phreng ba bsnams //
T02D1436:233a-14: phyag rgya drug ldan mgo bo'i phreng //
T02D1436:233a-15: spyan gsum sna tshogs rdo rje can //
T02D1436:233a-16: sna tshogs padma nyi mar gnas //
T02D1436:233a-17: 'jigs byed dus mtshan bcas par dgod //
T02D1436:233a-18: g-yas brkyang ba yi zhabs kyis bcibs //
T02D1436:233a-19: rdo rje dril bu ral par ldan //
T02D1436:233a-20: gang cing mi bskyod spyi bo'i gtsug / stag gi pags pas yang dag bcings //
T02D1436:233a-21: dpa' bo'i rdo rje phag mo ni //
T02D1436:233b-0: @233b spyan gsum dmar zhing mgo phreng ldan //
T02D1436:233b-1: rdo rje thod pa khrag gis bkang //
T02D1436:233b-2: rked rgyun dum bus mtshan pa 'dzin //
T02D1436:233b-3: phyogs kyi gos la phyag rgya lnga //
T02D1436:233b-4: dbu skra grol zhing sangs rgyas gtsug /'di ltar skad cig gis rdzogs pa'i //
T02D1436:233b-5: bdag nyid lus ni bsgom par bya //
T02D1436:233b-6: ye shes lnga yi rang bzhin gzugs //
T02D1436:233b-7: sangs rgyas 'od zer rnam par spro //
T02D1436:233b-8: spyod yul gcig gi sems kyis su //
T02D1436:233b-9: 'di nyid kho na yun ring bsam //
T02D1436:233b-11: chos dbyings rgyal mtshan yang dag sbyor //
T02D1436:233b-12: gnyis gnyis sbyor ba bde las phyung //
T02D1436:233b-13: dga' ba zag pa'i phun tshogs kyis//
T02D1436:233b-14: rang rig dga' bas yongs su khengs //
T02D1436:233b-15: zag pas skyed par byed pa gang //
T02D1436:233b-16: des ni rgya chen yid la byed //
T02D1436:233b-18: 'di ltar rtag tu sgom pa pos //
T02D1436:233b-19: 'od gsal rjes su dran par bya //
T02D1436:233b-20: sna tshogs padma nyi ma dang //
T02D1436:233b-21: 'jigs byed dang ni dus mtshan no //
T02D1436:233b-22: sdug ma bdag mo mkha' nor bu //
T02D1436:233b-23: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga yi 'og / sku dang yan lag mchog dang ni //
T02D1436:233b-24: zla ba thig le n'a da rnams //
T02D1436:233b-25: 'di rnams rim gyis mi snang gzhug / ji ltar me long dbus kyi rlung //
T02D1436:233b-26: thams cad thim par gyur pa ltar //
T02D1436:233b-27: yang dag mtha' ru yang nas yang //
T02D1436:233b-28: de bzhin rnal 'byor rab tu gzhug / grub thob rdo rje dril bu pas mdzad pa'i /
T02D1436:233b-29: bde mchog lhan skyes kyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so /
T02D1436:233b-31: // / pandita rdo rje gdan pa ni ska lam ka'i zhal snga nas /
